-- Oil Leak From Yemen Pipeline Explosion Was Minimal, Korea National Says
-- B y   S h i n h y e   K a n g
-- 2010-11-03T00:21:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-03/oil-leak-from-yemen-pipeline-explosion-was-minimal-korea-national-says.html
An oil leak from a pipeline in Yemem
operated by Korea National Oil Corp. was minimal, Kelvin Han, a
spokesman at the state-run South Korean explorer, said by phone
today. An explosion struck the pipeline yesterday.  For Related News and Information:  To contact the reporter on this story:
